DESCRIPTION:One map, complete match, essential building categories, limited types/pets/events, bots, ending, wishlist and feedback CTAs.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:store-page-target-20260824@personality-panic
DTSTAMP:20260720T120000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260824
