END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:nextfest-stay-withdraw-20260908@personality-panic
DTSTAMP:20260720T120000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260908
SUMMARY:Internal gate — stay in or withdraw from October Next Fest
DESCRIPTION:Stay only if the demo can represent the game well and remaining risks are polish rather than fundamental design.
END:VEVENT
