BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:launch-gate-20261027@personality-panic
DTSTAMP:20260720T120000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261027
SUMMARY:Personality Panic November launch go / no-go
DESCRIPTION:Decide from full-game readiness, demo behavior, wishlist quality, creator commitments, support capacity, and conservative sales expectations.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:release-candidate-lock-20261103@personality-panic
DTSTAMP:20260720T120000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261103
SUMMARY:Target — lock Personality Panic release candidate
DESCRIPTION:No content changes without a documented blocker and rollback plan.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:final-launch-approval-20261116@personality-panic
DTSTAMP:20260720T120000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261116
SUMMARY:Final founder launch approval
DESCRIPTION:Confirm build, store, discount, support, creator calendar, rollback plan, and launch-week availability.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:personality-panic-launch-20261117@personality-panic
DTSTAMP:20260720T120000Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20261117T100000
SUMMARY:PROVISIONAL — Personality Panic Steam launch
DESCRIPTION:Working plan: $19.99 base price with one 15–25% launch discount lasting 14 days and covering Black Friday.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:black-friday-20261127@personality-panic
DTSTAMP:20260720T120000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261127
SUMMARY:Black Friday — reuse the active launch offer
DESCRIPTION:Use launch reviews, clips, creator coverage, and player stories. Do not plan an immediate second 50% discount.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:two-week-launch-review-20261201@personality-panic
DTSTAMP:20260720T120000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261201
SUMMARY:Personality Panic two-week launch review
DESCRIPTION:Review sales, wishlist conversion, reviews, refunds, crashes, acquisition sources, creator performance, and support load.
END:VEVENT
